</sense> <sense n="4" xml:id="D4"> translate: <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> rapere </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> abripere </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> abstrahere </t:quote></cit> mentem vel animum (alicujus e corpore), ob admirationem, ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይሰልብ፡ አልባበ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Lit." loc="173,3">Lit. 173,3</ref>; (arca splendore suo) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተሀይድ፡ አዕይንተ፡ ወትሰልብ፡ ልበ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Kebr. Nag." loc="17">Kebr. Nag. 17</ref>; ob terrorem, Lud. e Ssal. Req. 
</sense> </sense>
               
